cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image and video denoising using a CNN architecture. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of self-similarities, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of a non-trainable layer to incorporate non-locality into the network suggests the involvement of machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of spatio-temporal volumes, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
